org.hibernate.ogm.jdbc.impl

Class NoopStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.jdbc.impl.NoopStatement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Statement, Wrapper

    public class NoopStatement
extends Object
implements Statement
    A Statement that does nothing.

    Hibernate OGM doesn't use JDBC connection so there aren't any statement to execute. This class has been introduce to solve compatibility issues with Hibernate 4.1.9.Final.

    Author:
    Davide D'Alto <davide@hibernate.org>
